  <brief_title>Efficacy of Antihistamine Dosing-up and add-on Treatment With H2-receptor Antagonist</brief_title>
  <acronym>OPEhRA</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized Open Labeled Trial to Compare the Efficacy of Antihistamine Dosing-up and add-on Treatment With H2-receptor Antagonist in Patients With Chronic Urticaria</official_title>
