    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adolescents and adults over 12 years

          -  Clinical diagnosis of chronic urticaria due to wheal reaction, itching, angioedema
             over 6 weeks

          -  Antihistamine 2 or 2 kinds of treatment for more than 2 weeks even if the symptoms are
             not controlled

          -  Those who do not have other chronic skin diseases

        Exclusion Criteria:
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
